snippet.title: Are We There Yet? -  Trailer
snippet.description:
Play for free: https://ramicreates.itch.io/awty

In 'Are We There Yet' you have to race across the highway to quickly reach a restroom for your children. 
Reach the next service station, causing as few traffic accidents as possible. If you fail, your car's carpet will be ruined!
